<br>
in the case where a worn item right clicks a mana regen spell using a buff slot (lunar whispers is a great example) it will stack.<br>
<br>
edit: btw, i think the best mana regen you can get from spells and gear (period) is around 43. not counting bard songs as i don't know the exact mana count. assuming that it's 11, like c2, you'd get to 77 mana regen per tick sitting down. at a maximum<br>
<br>
that's 15 for FT. 14 for KEI. 9 for potg and mots/h. 11 for bard song. 23 for sit. and 5 for boon of recovery/lunar whispers (that value is wrong, but close i think). 3 for MC.<br>
<br>
it's close to 80 per tick anyways.<br>
<br>
shamans on the other hand get over 100 per tick with torpor and canni.<br>
<br>
really makes ya think.<br>
